## ⚠️ Limitations / Caveats
- The openai-whisper package is inference-oriented; internal APIs may change—pin version (already pinned).
- Loss function is approximate; real pretraining uses complex sampling and multilingual tokens.
- No advanced features: curriculum, scheduler, gradient clipping, proper tokenizer BOS/EOT handling nuances.
- WER metric is optional & naive (not language-normalized).

